room_title: Escape room "The Queen" by Escape Long Beach in Orange County
room_description: Strange disappearances paired with ghost sightings around the Queen Mary have left the cops puzzled, so we need you, the best paranormal investigators since the Ghost Busters, to find out where these missing people have gone. A local psychic has a lead, believing the ghost of Queen Mary is collecting souls to sail her ship again. It’s up to you to find a way into her chambers and save the lost souls–without becoming trapped yourselves.
